Apple made a major slip Wednesday when it accidentally included hardware identifiers in software code linking to numerous unannounced products.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/08/Golden-Apple-Logo.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1013591" /><br/>
The leaked information provided <em>MacRumors</em> with concrete evidence of Apple's hardware development across multiple product categories. Here's everything that was confirmed through the code discoveries:<br/>
<br/>
<ul><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/homepod-mini-new-chip/">New HomePod mini with updated chip</a> – New model with S-series processor.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/new-apple-tv-coming-later-this-year-with-a17-pro-chip/">New Apple TV with A17 Pro chip</a> – Substantial upgrade from current A15 Bionic.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/apple-still-working-on-studio-display-2/">Apple Studio Display 2</a> – Next-gen Apple monitor with J427 codename.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/ipad-mini-a19-pro-chip/">New iPad mini with A19 Pro chip</a> – Using same processor as iPhone 17 Pro models.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/14/new-low-cost-ipad-feature-a18-chip/">New low-cost iPad with A18 chip</a> – expected to launch in the spring.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/apple-code-confirms-vision-pro-with-m5-chip/"</a>Apple Vision Pro with M5 chip</a> – Second-generation headset, settling chip confusion.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/apple-watch-s11-chip-info/">2025 Apple Watch chip details</a> – Similar T8310 architecture as current models.</li><br/>
</ul>Meanwhile, <em>Bloomberg</em> separately reported Wednesday on Apple's smart home ambitions. The company is developing a <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/apple-home-security-camera/">Ring-like security camera</a>, while its <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/apple-smart-home-hub-2026/">iPad-style smart home hub</a> isn't coming until mid-2026. A tabletop robot companion with a movable display is also <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/13/apple-launching-robot-virtual-companion-in-2027/">planned for 2027</a>, featuring an enhanced Siri powered by large language models.<br/>This article, &quot;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/14/every-apple-secret-that-leaked-yesterday/">Every Apple Secret That Leaked Yesterday</a>&quot; first appeared on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com">MacRumors.com</a><br/><br/><a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/every-apple-secret-that-leaked-yesterday.2463353/">Discuss this article</a> in our forums<br/><br/>